skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: New Jersey 101.5 News Flash Briefing brings you the latest news about the Garden State — headlines about politics, business, crime, events and the stories that affect your life every day. Want to know more? Listen now and read the latest at NJ1015.com and on the New Jersey 101.5 app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
